The evidence with the title 'ATF: 70 percent of guns found in Mexico come from US | TheHill ' says Apr 26, 2012  ... Nearly 70 percent of all guns found in Mexico came from the U.S. over the past four years , according to data released by the federal government on thursday . More than 68000 of the 99691 firearms that were recovered between 2007 and 2011 , and submitted to the Bureau Of Alcohol, Tobacco, Firearms  ... 
